{
  "video_id": "lVNZBHIXMlw",
  "title": "NOVUS Summit at United Nations presents Jacque Fresco award for city design.",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 596.0,
      "end_time": 4300.0,
      "text": "NOVUS Summit, United Nations 07.17.2016"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4301.0,
      "end_time": 7636.0,
      "text": "presented Jacque Fresco an award for city design"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10440.0,
      "end_time": 11280.0,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12460.0,
      "end_time": 14480.0,
      "text": "In 1974,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15200.0,
      "end_time": 18820.0,
      "text": "Jacque Fresco appeared on Larry King’s show."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19400.0,
      "end_time": 21800.0,
      "text": "1974!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22200.0,
      "end_time": 24480.0,
      "text": "This is how the interview begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27620.0,
      "end_time": 31420.0,
      "text": "[Larry King] My guest is an extraordinary Miamian: Dr. Jacque Fresco."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31876.0,
      "end_time": 34172.0,
      "text": "I could go through all the things that Dr. Fresco has done."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34280.0,
      "end_time": 36935.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a social engineer, industrial engineer, designer, inventor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38250.0,
      "end_time": 40560.0,
      "text": "consultant - was a consultant - for Rotorcraft Helicopter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40670.0,
      "end_time": 42941.0,
      "text": "Director of Scientific Research Laboratories Los Angeles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43580.0,
      "end_time": 44960.0,
      "text": "designed and copyrighted various items,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45255.0,
      "end_time": 47600.0,
      "text": "ranging from drafting instruments to X-ray units,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48787.0,
      "end_time": 52440.0,
      "text": "has had works published in the Architectural Record, Popular Mechanics, Saturday Review,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53530.0,
      "end_time": 56621.0,
      "text": "and has been a technical and psychological consultant to the motion picture industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56730.0,
      "end_time": 59747.0,
      "text": "member of the Air Force design and development unit at Wright Field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60320.0,
      "end_time": 63501.0,
      "text": "developed the electrostatic anti-icing systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63926.0,
      "end_time": 66240.0,
      "text": "designed prefabricated aluminum houses…"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66400.0,
      "end_time": 67913.0,
      "text": "What does it say on your driver’s license?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69144.0,
      "end_time": 70166.0,
      "text": "What is the occupation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70547.0,
      "end_time": 74166.0,
      "text": "[Jacque Fresco] Industrial designer… social engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74756.0,
      "end_time": 76240.0,
      "text": "- Does it bug you that"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76523.0,
      "end_time": 78535.0,
      "text": "people, when they talk about Jacque Fresco in Miami,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78652.0,
      "end_time": 82455.0,
      "text": "say that he&#39;s someone who&#39;s too far ahead of his time, his thinking is-"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82941.0,
      "end_time": 86609.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not ready for advanced kind of thinking, of that type."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87230.0,
      "end_time": 90467.0,
      "text": "- I imagine every creative person in every field"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90578.0,
      "end_time": 92344.0,
      "text": "encounters that sort of problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92603.0,
      "end_time": 94356.0,
      "text": "No, it doesn&#39;t. I can&#39;t afford it;"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94584.0,
      "end_time": 96350.0,
      "text": "there’s too many things that are important."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97790.0,
      "end_time": 100178.0,
      "text": "For the past 85 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100726.0,
      "end_time": 103396.0,
      "text": "Jacque Fresco has blessed us"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103686.0,
      "end_time": 107784.0,
      "text": "with his unwavering commitment and uncompromising work"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108246.0,
      "end_time": 110792.0,
      "text": "to re-engineer a better future."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111809.0,
      "end_time": 114480.0,
      "text": "He is the founder of The Venus Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114289.0,
      "end_time": 117200.0,
      "text": "which integrates science and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117513.0,
      "end_time": 121210.0,
      "text": "into a comprehensive plan for a new society"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121224.0,
      "end_time": 125150.0,
      "text": "based on human and environmental concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125729.0,
      "end_time": 129809.0,
      "text": "The Venus Project proposes a system in which automation and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134806.0,
      "text": "are intelligently integrated into a holistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 137310.0,
      "text": "socio-economic design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137624.0,
      "end_time": 141950.0,
      "text": "where the primary function is to maximize the quality of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142750.0,
      "end_time": 144467.0,
      "text": "rather than profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145427.0,
      "end_time": 149784.0,
      "text": "Jacque Fresco has recently celebrated his 100th birthday!"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150843.0,
      "end_time": 155950.0,
      "text": "And he couldn&#39;t join us today but he is watching us right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156609.0,
      "end_time": 160541.0,
      "text": "On behalf of all of us Mr. Fresco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162264.0,
      "end_time": 165575.0,
      "text": "thank you and your partner Roxanne Meadows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165680.0,
      "end_time": 169156.0,
      "text": "for your vision, your tireless research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169347.0,
      "end_time": 171803.0,
      "text": "extraordinary life achievements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171956.0,
      "end_time": 174790.0,
      "text": "and everlasting legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 175304.0,
      "end_time": 178313.0,
      "text": "Mr. Fresco, we are beginning to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178916.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "We are beginning to get ready for this advanced kind of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 183292.0,
      "end_time": 187150.0,
      "text": "We are getting there, and you have been a critical force"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 187280.0,
      "end_time": 188467.0,
      "text": "for that change."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188867.0,
      "end_time": 193606.0,
      "text": "Please, a warm round of applause for Mr. Jacque Fresco!"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194500.0,
      "end_time": 196843.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197729.0,
      "end_time": 200000.0,
      "text": "This is Julio, who will pick up the award."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 203427.0,
      "end_time": 205267.0,
      "text": "[Jacque Fresco] I am deeply honored"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205569.0,
      "end_time": 208732.0,
      "text": "and appreciate this prestigious recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208990.0,
      "end_time": 211550.0,
      "text": "for my work with city design."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212180.0,
      "end_time": 215150.0,
      "text": "These cities are part of a broader picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215433.0,
      "end_time": 218180.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve dedicated my life towards."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 218498.0,
      "end_time": 221840.0,
      "text": "My aim was to identify the root causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222310.0,
      "end_time": 224683.0,
      "text": "of the problems we face today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 224910.0,
      "end_time": 227901.0,
      "text": "and propose alternatives for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228363.0,
      "end_time": 231790.0,
      "text": "I concluded it was the social design itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 232190.0,
      "end_time": 235624.0,
      "text": "that creates the unnecessary human suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 235975.0,
      "end_time": 239581.0,
      "text": "when at the same time we have the technical ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 239723.0,
      "end_time": 243993.0,
      "text": "and the resources that can surpass our present conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244621.0,
      "end_time": 247298.0,
      "text": "[Roxanne Meadows] Jacque proposes a new holistic"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 247403.0,
      "end_time": 252970.0,
      "text": "socioeconomic design he calls a Resource Based Economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 252443.0,
      "end_time": 255280.0,
      "text": "in which the methods of science and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 255569.0,
      "end_time": 260128.0,
      "text": "are integrated to maximize the quality of life for all people."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 260603.0,
      "end_time": 264732.0,
      "text": "This project also introduces a set of practical values"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 265330.0,
      "end_time": 268646.0,
      "text": "to give people a better understanding of our relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 268836.0,
      "end_time": 271784.0,
      "text": "to one another, and the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 271938.0,
      "end_time": 275120.0,
      "text": "One fundamental premise is that we work toward"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 275280.0,
      "end_time": 279335.0,
      "text": "having all of the Earth’s resources as the common heritage"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 279458.0,
      "end_time": 281107.0,
      "text": "of all the world&#39;s people."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 281320.0,
      "end_time": 285729.0,
      "text": "It requires the intelligent management of Earth&#39;s resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 286300.0,
      "end_time": 289316.0,
      "text": "in order to achieve a high standard of living"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 289480.0,
      "end_time": 292369.0,
      "text": "for the entire global population."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292480.0,
      "end_time": 295735.0,
      "text": "Anything less will simply result in a continuation"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 295840.0,
      "end_time": 298750.0,
      "text": "of the same problems we have today."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 298916.0,
      "end_time": 303581.0,
      "text": "This also incorporates a systems approach to architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303858.0,
      "end_time": 306135.0,
      "text": "which is in harmony with nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 306393.0,
      "end_time": 309421.0,
      "text": "All cities will be designed to operate"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 309606.0,
      "end_time": 312215.0,
      "text": "with a minimum expenditure of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 312326.0,
      "end_time": 315643.0,
      "text": "using the cleanest technology available."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 317489.0,
      "end_time": 322203.0,
      "text": "We are now organizing to initiate the very first city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 322720.0,
      "end_time": 326941.0,
      "text": "under our recently formed 501c3 organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 327126.0,
      "end_time": 330120.0,
      "text": "called Resource Based Economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330935.0,
      "end_time": 333870.0,
      "text": "We welcome your inquiry and participation"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333993.0,
      "end_time": 337396.0,
      "text": "to help build this new innovative city."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 339330.0,
      "end_time": 342283.0,
      "text": "Now we operate under the name The Venus Project"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 342393.0,
      "end_time": 344280.0,
      "text": "out of Venus Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 344584.0,
      "end_time": 348172.0,
      "text": "We invite you to learn more about this positive alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 348418.0,
      "end_time": 351156.0,
      "text": "at theVenusProject.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 351360.0,
      "end_time": 353403.0,
      "text": "Thank you for this opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 353660.0,
      "end_time": 357300.0,
      "text": "Again, thank you very much for this award."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 359304.0,
      "end_time": 362490.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 364338.0,
      "end_time": 366680.0,
      "text": "On behalf of Jacque Fresco and the Venus Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 367649.0,
      "end_time": 369400.0,
      "text": "we thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 370000.0,
      "end_time": 372627.0,
      "text": "[Applause]"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 378744.0,
      "end_time": 381680.0,
      "text": "That was really inspiring, it’s amazing to see what’s going on there."
    }
  ]
}